.TH SG-CTL 1 "June 2026" "Snoop Guard 1.1.0-dev"
.SH NAME
sg-ctl \- inspect and control Snoop Guard
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sg-ctl
[\fB--json\fR] [status|health|recent [N]|watch|reload]
.SH EXIT STATUS
Zero indicates success. health returns 2 for degraded monitoring and 3 when a
monitor is unavailable. Other failures return nonzero.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sg-daemon (1)
